(defn dispatch-nodes-to-state [nodes & {:keys [depth] :or {depth 0}}]
  (doseq [node nodes]
    (if (= (node :type) "folder")
      (do
        ; (prn node)
        (re-frame/dispatch [:set-nodes (conj {:depth depth} node)])
        (dispatch-nodes-to-state (node :children) :depth (inc depth)))

      (do
        (re-frame/dispatch [:set-nodes (conj {:depth depth} node)])
        (dispatch-nodes-to-state (node :children) :depth (inc depth))
        ))))
